 Justification:
 W12057 UNMANNED AND AUTONOMOUS GROUND SYSTEMS is a new start within the Robotics and Applique Systems program in FY 2027. FY 2027 Base Procurement dollars in the amount of $20.325
 million will award the production of unmanned robotics systems, procure their associated support elements, initiate fielding, conduct production testing, and fund related Government Program Management
 expenses.

 W20897 Autonomous Transport Vehicle (ATV): FY 2027 Base Procurement dollars in the amount of $41.602 million will fund the refurbishment of test assets, procurement of new systems, and program related
