 6, 7, and ESB 8.

 2) The Outfitting and Post Delivery amounts in the Prior Years column represent NDSF BLI 5000 for ESD 1, ESD 2, and ESB 3 as well as SCN BLI 5110 for the ESB 4 and ESB 5; and ESB 6 outfitting.


